import { Hero, Container, Heading, Button, Image} from 'react-bulma-components';

    <Hero.Body>
      <Container className="has-text-centered">
        <Heading size={1}>Live with Confidence</Heading>
        <Heading subtitle size={4}>
          Jos√© Mourinho brings confidence to pan-African Sanlam campaign.
        </Heading>
        <Button color="warning" size="medium" rounded>
          View project
        </Button>
      </Container>
    </Hero.Body>
  </Hero>
);

export default Header;
